.DT 
zap_stat_cache 
Discworld living help 
zap_stat_cache 

Name
.SI 5
zap_stat_cache - Reset's the stat cache.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void zap_stat_cache(string stat);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Resets the stat cache back to its original empty stat.  This is used
in the stat changeing thingys to make sure that the skills are correctly
modified by the newly changed stats.  If stat is 0 it will zap the entire
array, if it is a string it will only zap the ones that that particular
stat has something to do with.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_stat_cache, query_skill_bonus
.EP
